articles.author: Robert Lea
articles.title: 'God's Hand' interstellar cloud reaches for the stars in new Dark Energy Camera image (video) - Space.com
articles.description: There is nothing supernatural about this celestial structure, but it is awe-inspiring nonetheless.
articles.content: The Dark Energy Camera (DECam) has captured an ominous and ghostly hand reaching from the Milky Way from a distant edge-on spiral galaxy. But don't panic; despite its nickname, "God's Hand," there is… [+4932 chars]
